question: Will 'Wish' gross over $55m over its 5-day opening weekend?
description:
This is a market on how much 'Wish' (2023) will gross domestically on its opening weekend. The “Domestic Weekend” tab on https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt11304740/ will be used to resolve this market once the values for the 5-day opening weekend (November 22 - November 26) are final (i.e. not studio estimates).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if ‘Wish' (2023) grosses more than $55,000,000 on its 5-day opening. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

Please note, this market will resolve according to the sum of the Box Office Mojo numbers under Domestic Daily for November 22-26, regardless of whether domestic refers to only the USA, or to USA and Canada, etc.

If there is no final data available by December 7, 2023, 11:59 PM ET, another credible resolution source will be chosen.

events.title: Box Office: Nov 22-26
events.description: qq

question: Sam Altman back on OpenAI board by Nov 30?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if it is announced Sam Altman will rejoin the OpenAI board by Nov 30, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No."

Note that an announcement before the end date that he will be rejoining the board will suffice to resolve this market to "Yes" regardless of when his rejoining goes into effect.

Confirmation should come from an official announcement made by OpenAI or Sam Altman himself, however a definitive consensus of credible media sources may be used.

question: Will the Hamas x Israel ceasefire last the full 4 days?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the first ceasefire between Hamas and Israel pursuant to a hostage/prisoner exchange deal after the creation of this market lasts at least 4 full days (96 consecutive hours). Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If no such ceasefire starts by December 31, 2023, 11:59 PM IST (Israeli Standard Time), this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be a consensus of credible information and reporting.
